title: Rental Income of Persons for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1939-1945 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1968. Data Are Billions Of Dollars At Annual Rates Source: Survey Of Current Business, August 1965 For Data Through 1962; July Issues Of Survey Of Current Business Are Used Thereafter.

This NBER data series m08277b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
